item.description:
This is an awesome and very fun Carly recording. Highly recommended if you love good pop music and you want the best of her pre-Emotion songs.

The original video was 10GB, looked good but had obvious and distracting banding. Basically the background looked pixelated. I fixed that and it looks much better now. I also included an info file with the setlist and I manually added chapters for each song.
